{"word":"G3423 - μνηστεύω - mnēsteúō - mnace-tyoo'-o - Espouse","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μνηστεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">mnēsteúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">mnace-tyoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Espouse</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நியமி"},{"paragraph":"to woo her and ask her in marriage"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a derivative of <a href=\"#/G3415 - μνάομαι - mnáomai - mnah'-om-ahee/3415\">G3415</a>; to <i>give a souvenir</i> (engagement present), that is, <i>betroth:</i> - espouse.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}